{
  "stem": "17426.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 88.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so when the doctor heard that I had my own instruments and just what I did in my first camp, in the first camp that I was in, Steineck, he agreed that I could come and after work I could do what I did in Steineck.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so I began to do that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But in time, there were more work than it was in Steineck, twice as much.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And also, he needed an assist, he needed some help for first aid.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he asked the commandant whether he would allow me-- him to take me in full-time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And so I was full-time dentist and first aid help.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Another break.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we spent from May through next April, this camp was-- also give me the opportunity to, during the day, at first, to work for a engineer of the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Workplace.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he also put me in the office, to draft things for him, to make copies of things that he has drafted, and to just generally work.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was a German member of the NSDAP, Nationalsozialistische Deutsche Arbeiterpartei, which is the Nazi party.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But somehow, he was a human being, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name was-- it escapes me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I will give it to you later.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I asked him, I-- when winter came, I ask him to-- our people were so poorly clad and cold.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I ask him whether we couldn't make a fire on the [NON-ENGLISH], keep a fire going so they could come in when they are frozen, their hands are frozen.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were carrying rails, iron rails, in wagons, push cars, with dirt and ties for the rails.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Whether they-- he couldn't allow to have a little fire, so they could come in and warm up for a few minutes and go back to work.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
